Name: Mon-Musu Master
About the game: *All characters in this game are 18 or older You can make all Mon-Musu join your team! Create your original party and save the world! A retro black-and-white RPG. Featuring countless Mon-Musu! Fight them, add them to your team, and beat the Dark Lord! System - An orthodox turn-based RPG! - Explore the map to find treasure! - A simple combat system! New to RPGs? No problem! - Beat the Mon-Musu and add them to your team! - Conversations can be skipped!
